## 1. Home Page Layout & Orchestration

### 1.1 Main Chat Interface Layout
**File: `src/pages/HomePage.jsx`**

**Key Concepts:**
- Layout orchestration and component composition
- Conditional rendering based on user selection
- Responsive design patterns

**Code Analysis:**
```jsx
// File: src/pages/HomePage.jsx
const HomePage = () => {
  const { selectedUser } = useChatStore();

  return (
    <div className="h-screen bg-base-200">
      <div className="flex items-center justify-center pt-20 px-4">
        <div className="bg-base-100 rounded-lg shadow-cl w-full max-w-6xl h-[calc(100vh-8rem)]">
          <div className="flex h-full rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
            <Sidebar />
            {!selectedUser ? <NoChatSelected /> : <ChatContainer />}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  );
};
```

**Learning Points:**
- **Conditional Rendering**: `{!selectedUser ? <NoChatSelected /> : <ChatContainer />}`
- **CSS Calculations**: `h-[calc(100vh-8rem)]` for dynamic height
- **Component Composition**: Breaking UI into reusable components
- **Flexbox Layout**: Responsive container structure

